OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCentral and
OL,6,Fsouthern England and Wales will remain
OL,7,Fcloudy this evening and overnight,
OL,8,Fwith further rain. Elsewhere there
OL,9,Fwill be clear spells, but with
OL,10,Fblustery showers in the far north and
OL,11,Fnorthwest. Mild and frost-free for all.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FCentral and southern England
OL,14,Fand Wales will hold onto outbreaks of
OL,15,Frain on Friday, heaviest in the west
OL,16,Flater. Brighter elsewhere with a few
OL,17,Fshowers. Mild, with mostly gentle
OL,18,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
